* 2.41千万像素[[尼康|尼康]]DX幅面[[CMOS|CMOS]][[感光元件|感光元件]]<ref name="WEBSITE">{{Cite web|url=http://imaging.nikon.com/lineup/dslr/d7100/|title=D7100|author=NIKON|accessdate=2013-10-17|archive-date=2013-04-29|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6GFEQQUKn?url=http://imaging.nikon.com/lineup/dslr/d7100/|dead-url=yes}}</REF> 
